            <div class="text">
              <strong>SALON PROPHETS</strong>, led by Founder &amp; CEO Robert Cass, is a leading consulting, marketing and training advisors to the salon industry. They bring more than 30 years of successful salon, spa and hospitality management and development experience combined with an endless commitment towards excellence.
               <br><br>
              Industry leaders such as Wella, Red Door Spas, Lifespa, Stillwater, Fantastic Sams, have all chosen to work with Salon Prophets because of their intimate knowledge and expertise of the salon market. They have developed Wella Premium Business Education program, SMBA – Salon Masters of Business Advancement and are the driving force behind Salon Savvy, The Art of Business Education.
               <br><br>
              Robert travels the continent as a keynote speaker, author and trainer educating and elevating the standards of today's salons. Working with leaders and teams Salon Prophets focuses on your business so it rewards you with the profits you deserve.
               <br><br>
              Salon Prophets is &quot;building business&quot;.
            </div>
